            "children": [
              {
                "text": "> The speaker's parents provided guidance on how to navigate a society with prevalent anti-Semitism. This advice was similar to the cautionary directions that African American parents often give to their children, emphasizing the need to remain inconspicuous to avoid discrimination and prejudice."
